KUSHONE abantu ababili nengane, kwalimala  abathathu ngesikhathi kutholana phezulu izimoto ezishayisane emgwaqweni, uN2, eMandeni ngoMgqibelo ekuseni. Kuthiwa kwenye yalezi zimoto ebinamalungu amathathu omndeni owodwa, kushone owesilisa, owesifazane nengane abebehamba nayo. Emotweni yesibili kulimale owesifazane nengane ephuthunyiswe esibhedlela. Okhulumela abezimo eziphuthumayo uMnuz Paul Herbst we-IPSS Medical Rescue, uthe ithimba labo lifike laxilonga abantu abebelimele endaweni yesigameko. “Ngenxa yendlela esifike isimo sibucayi ngayo, kuphoqeleke ukuthi kuvalwe umgwaqo ukuze sixilonge kahle abantu abebelimele kanzima engozini,” kubeka uHerbst. Okhulumela amaphoyisa KwaZulu-Natal uCaptain Nqobile Gwala, usiqinisekisile isigameko sokushayisana kwezimoto ngoMgqibelo. “Ayikaziwa imbangela yengozi. Amaphoyisa aseMandeni aphenya icala lokubulala ngokungenhloso,” kubeka uCaptain Gwala. Khonamanjalo kushayisane izimoto ezintathu emgwaqweni uN2 eTinely Manor eduze kwendawo okulungiswa kuyo lo mgwaqo. Eyodwa yalezi zimoto ishe yangqongqa. UCaptain Gwala, uthe amaphoyisa asesiteshini saseMhlali athole umbiko ngale ngozi. Uthe akukho muntu olimale kule ngozi.  